Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on using sound as a sensor modality to generate virtual camera images, which falls under the domain of sound processing and analysis.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper discusses generating 2D and 3D representations of the world, which is a core topic in computer vision.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper involves designing a system that can process sound signals and generate visual representations, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper involves training a neural network to generate visual representations from sound signals, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper involves training a neural network to generate visual representations from sound signals, which falls under the domain of machine learning.
